address2: 26th Floor Room 2608, Greenfield Tower 1 Science Museum Road, TST East
longBusinessSummary: China Environmental Resources Group Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the sale of recycled metals, motor vehicles, and related accessories in the People's Republic of China and internationally. It operates through Trading of Recycled Metals, Trading of Motor Vehicles and Related Accessories, Property Investment, Provision of Financial Services, Sale of Golden Flower Tea Products, Securities Trading and Investment, and Sales of Plantation Material and Products segments. The company also engages in car parking spaces rental, money lending, and securities trading and investment business; and operates green business of research, development, and application of technologies and solutions. In addition, it manufacture, sells, and trades products, materials, and systems and services for green market including the environmental markets, agricultural markets, organic markets, and green technology markets; and operates hotel business. Further, the company offers securities brokerage, and margin and loan financing services; and engages in sale of mobile phones and electronic components, as well as manufactures and sells apparel labels and packaging printing products. China Environmental Resources Group Limited was formerly known as Benefun International Holdings Limited and changed its name to China Environmental Resources Group Limited in December 2009. The company was founded in 1986 and is based in Kowloon, Hong Kong.
